profile_positions.description:
- Media relations and PR, with emphasis on strategy, issues management and relationship-building with strategic journalists;  
- Manager of seven professionals, with direct report to the CEO;
- Executive communications and media training;
- Budget planning and management;
- Responsible for internal communications (serving over 600 employees in multiple locations);
- Brand journalism and content development: publisher and editor of four in-house, multimedia news outlets distributed weekly to thousands of subscribers nationwide.

- Media relations strategy and implementation, positioning the company’s headhunters as thought-leaders in talent recruitment, career counseling and HR management;
- Executive communications, media training and message development;
- Content development and website management;
- Participation in the re-branding, new visual identity and external positioning of two HR-focused consultancies (Case Consulting and Thomas Case & Associados);
- Active support on marketing communications, events and employee engagement.

- Responsible for the overall management and content feed for the Entertainment (TV, cinema, music, arts, celebrities) channel;
- Coordination of special coverages and projects;
- Management and negotiation of promotions for clients and readers (working with film distributors, record labels, sporting goods suppliers);
- Support to the corporate PR department with promotional press releases and media outreach.
